<h2 class='balance-text'>Implement ticketing system</h2>
<p>Tools like Zendesk help employees report issues around specific topics. Stop getting random emails about it being too cold or too hot. Have it categorized and prioritized in a ticketing system. Then you can report to leadership which issues are the biggest problem.</p>

