<h2 class='balance-text'>Standardize the interview, hiring, and department lifecycle</h2>
<p>Increase the objectivity and data entry of the human capitalize lifecycle. Make sure that the interview process is the same for every person who is interviewed and that the same questions are asked. Score and keep track of how well people interview and whether those questions lead to highly engaged, productive employees.</p>

